1     PIN_FLD_DESCR           STR [0] "This parameter specifies whether to store objects referenced by price objects in memory in the CM cache when the CM starts. Objects referenced by price objects include BEIDs, GLIDs, tax suppliers, event types, service types, and RUMs. The value for this entry can be 0(The CM caches objects that are referenced by price objectsin the CM cache every time a price list is committed.) or 1((Default) The CM caches objects that are referenced by price objects one time when the CM starts.)"
